onchain_metadata.name: Wen PSB Discord OG
Description: "Wen PSB Discord" are loyalty tokens to reward
supporters who started from the bottom.
Back when PSB was just a p and hadn't earned the right
to capitalize yet. For those who watched him contribute
and grow while providing nothing in return for their stake,
most of the time. Boris did feed them though,
starving for some type of return, he gave them pizza.
There was always a need for something more though.
A place where they could bombard Boris,
with questions about Cardano, stakepools, and more pizza.
PSB succumbed to the pressure and committed to
spinning up a server on the weekend of 2/24/2023.
We have yet to see how this plays out but
hodlers of this token will rule the server
and get special drops on Tosi!
